welcome_message_body: Welcome to Warwick, a charming city known for its rich history, beautiful architecture, and friendly locals. Get ready to explore and immerse yourself in all that this wonderful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at West Midlands International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at West Midlands International Airport handles all freight and logistics operations.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by connecting to the network 'WMIA Free WiFi'.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Birmingham Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Birmingham Airport primarily serves low-cost and holiday airlines.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Birmingham Airport serves a mix of domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Northampton Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Northampton Airport is exclusively for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
